jltl2dstar

Class DRA

  • java.lang.Object
    • jltl2dstar.DA
      • jltl2dstar.DRA

  • public class DRA
extends DA
    A class representing a deterministic Rabin automaton.

    For details on the template parameters, see class DA.

    The DRA can be considered as a Streett automaton, if a flag is set.
